tracker-form-bind=3D"true">Sign Me Up</button></div></form></div><h2 id=3D"=
h-fonts-vs-typography-vs-typeface">Fonts vs. Typography vs. Typeface </h2><=
div class=3D"text-formatting"><p>Someone should make a folksong about the d=
ifference between typefaces, fonts, and typography. These things are differ=
ent, and they aren=E2=80=99t interchangeable (even though the lines blur).&=
nbsp;</p><p>But I=E2=80=99m not a folk songwriter, so I=E2=80=99ll plot out=
 the descriptions in words.</p></div><h3 id=3D"h-typefaces">Typefaces </h3>=
<div class=3D"text-formatting"><p>You=E2=80=99ve been calling typefaces =E2=
=80=9Cfonts=E2=80=9D for years.&nbsp;</p><p>It=E2=80=99s okay. You didn=E2=
=80=99t know you were confused (neither did I).&nbsp;</p><p>To clear things=
 up, a typeface (also called a type family) is the name of a collection of =
fonts.</p><p>Typeface example: <strong>Roboto</strong>.</p><p>A typeface is=
 the base style=E2=80=94it=E2=80=99s how a font looks without styling appli=
ed to it.&nbsp;</p></div><div><figure class=3D"wp-block-image"><img height=
=3D"158" width=3D"1250" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"https://wp.klientboost.com/=
wp-content/uploads/2021/07/img_61005dffa26f1.png" alt=3D"The difference bet=
ween Roboto and Merriweather typefaces"><figcaption class=3D"wp-element-cap=
tion">The difference between Roboto and Merriweather typefaces</figcaption>=
</figure></div><h3 id=3D"h-fonts">Fonts </h3><div class=3D"text-formatting"=
><p>Fonts are characteristics of a typeface. There are several font variati=
ons for a single typeface. Fonts describe the weight, width, and style of a=
 collection of characters within one typeface.&nbsp;</p><p>For example, the=
se are Roboto fonts:</p><p>Roboto normal</p><p>Roboto thin/<em>italics</em>=
</p><p>Roboto light/<em>italics</em></p><p>Roboto medium/<em>italics&nbsp;<=
/em></p><p><strong>Roboto bold/</strong><strong><em>italics</em></strong></=
p><p>Roboto black/<em>italics</em></p></div><div><figure class=3D"wp-block-=
image"><img height=3D"956" width=3D"1600" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"https://w=
p.klientboost.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/img_61005dffe2a30.png" alt=3D"=
The six fonts of the typeface Roboto=E2=80=93 source "><figcaption class=3D=
"wp-element-caption">Typeface =E2=80=9CRoboto=E2=80=9D has six fonts =F0=9F=
=A4=AF =E2=80=93 <a href=3D"https://snowball.digital/blog/what-is-the-diffe=
rence-between-a-font-and-a-typeface" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer no=
opener">source</a> </figcaption></figure></div><div class=3D"text-formattin=
g"><p>Fonts take us back to the 15th century, long before computers (or eve=
n typewriters) were invented. In printing, setting type meant arranging a c=
ollection of metal fonts on a plate.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>Today, fonts are cod=
es you install on your website=E2=80=99s back end so you can display a type=
face. And that=E2=80=99s why the word =E2=80=9Cfont=E2=80=9D has blurred in=
to the typeface realm to mean =E2=80=9Cthe style of letters.=E2=80=9D</p><p=
>We use CSS (cascading style sheets) code to style our web typefaces.&nbsp;=
</p><p><strong>font-family: Roboto; </strong>(setting the typeface)</p><p><=
strong>font-weight: bold; </strong>&nbsp;(setting the typeface style)</p><p=
><strong>font-size: 32px; </strong>(setting the typeface size)</p><p>The fo=
nts you choose affect the <strong>readability</strong> of your <a href=3D"h=
ttps://klientboost.com/landing-page-design/" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noref=
errer noopener">landing page or website design</a> and make a <a href=3D"ht=
tp://conversionxl.com/first-impressions-matter-the-importance-of-great-visu=
al-design/" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">vital first impre=
ssion</a> on your visitors.</p><p>Fonts communicate tone and mood.&nbsp;</p=
><p>A sans serif Roboto typeface set in a bold font is more serious in tone=
 than a serif font like Merriweather set in light italics.</p></div><div><f=
igure class=3D"wp-block-image"><img height=3D"158" width=3D"1222" loading=
=3D"lazy" src=3D"https://wp.klientboost.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/img_=
61005e0173ef5.png" alt=3D"A serious font versus a whimsical font"><figcapti=
